{
  "video_id": "AOEQ9GteWbg",
  "title": "Danny Hillis: The Internet could crash. We need a Plan B",
  "es": 1,
  "json": [
    {
      "index": 1,
      "start_time": 0.0,
      "end_time": 7000.0,
      "text": "Translator: Joseph Geni Reviewer: Morton Bast"
    },
    {
      "index": 2,
      "start_time": 15863.0,
      "end_time": 18929.0,
      "text": "So, this book that I have in my hand"
    },
    {
      "index": 3,
      "start_time": 18929.0,
      "end_time": 22863.0,
      "text": "is a directory of everybody who had an email address"
    },
    {
      "index": 4,
      "start_time": 22863.0,
      "end_time": 26381.0,
      "text": "in 1982. (Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 5,
      "start_time": 26382.0,
      "end_time": 30670.0,
      "text": "Actually, it&#39;s deceptively large."
    },
    {
      "index": 6,
      "start_time": 30670.0,
      "end_time": 33504.0,
      "text": "There&#39;s actually only about 20 people on each page,"
    },
    {
      "index": 7,
      "start_time": 33504.0,
      "end_time": 35394.0,
      "text": "because we have the name, address"
    },
    {
      "index": 8,
      "start_time": 35394.0,
      "end_time": 38486.0,
      "text": "and telephone number of every single person."
    },
    {
      "index": 9,
      "start_time": 38487.0,
      "end_time": 40670.0,
      "text": "And, in fact, everybody&#39;s listed twice,"
    },
    {
      "index": 10,
      "start_time": 40670.0,
      "end_time": 45228.0,
      "text": "because it&#39;s sorted once by name and once by email address."
    },
    {
      "index": 11,
      "start_time": 45228.0,
      "end_time": 48129.0,
      "text": "Obviously a very small community."
    },
    {
      "index": 12,
      "start_time": 48129.0,
      "end_time": 51559.0,
      "text": "There were only two other Dannys on the Internet then."
    },
    {
      "index": 13,
      "start_time": 51560.0,
      "end_time": 53160.0,
      "text": "I knew them both."
    },
    {
      "index": 14,
      "start_time": 53160.0,
      "end_time": 54916.0,
      "text": "We didn&#39;t all know each other,"
    },
    {
      "index": 15,
      "start_time": 54916.0,
      "end_time": 58290.0,
      "text": "but we all kind of trusted each other,"
    },
    {
      "index": 16,
      "start_time": 58290.0,
      "end_time": 61827.0,
      "text": "and that basic feeling of trust"
    },
    {
      "index": 17,
      "start_time": 61827.0,
      "end_time": 64414.0,
      "text": "permeated the whole network,"
    },
    {
      "index": 18,
      "start_time": 64414.0,
      "end_time": 66771.0,
      "text": "and there was a real sense that"
    },
    {
      "index": 19,
      "start_time": 66771.0,
      "end_time": 69777.0,
      "text": "we could depend on each other to do things."
    },
    {
      "index": 20,
      "start_time": 69777.0,
      "end_time": 73352.0,
      "text": "So just to give you an idea of the level of trust in this community,"
    },
    {
      "index": 21,
      "start_time": 73352.0,
      "end_time": 74977.0,
      "text": "let me tell you what it was like"
    },
    {
      "index": 22,
      "start_time": 74977.0,
      "end_time": 79820.0,
      "text": "to register a domain name in the early days."
    },
    {
      "index": 23,
      "start_time": 79820.0,
      "end_time": 81711.0,
      "text": "Now, it just so happened that I got to register"
    },
    {
      "index": 24,
      "start_time": 81712.0,
      "end_time": 84172.0,
      "text": "the third domain name on the Internet."
    },
    {
      "index": 25,
      "start_time": 84172.0,
      "end_time": 85820.0,
      "text": "So I could have anything I wanted"
    },
    {
      "index": 26,
      "start_time": 85820.0,
      "end_time": 90264.0,
      "text": "other than bbn.com and symbolics.com."
    },
    {
      "index": 27,
      "start_time": 90265.0,
      "end_time": 93679.0,
      "text": "So I picked think.com, but then I thought,"
    },
    {
      "index": 28,
      "start_time": 93679.0,
      "end_time": 96665.0,
      "text": "you know, there&#39;s a lot of really interesting names out there."
    },
    {
      "index": 29,
      "start_time": 96665.0,
      "end_time": 100874.0,
      "text": "Maybe I should register a few extras just in case."
    },
    {
      "index": 30,
      "start_time": 100874.0,
      "end_time": 104158.0,
      "text": "And then I thought, \"Nah, that wouldn&#39;t be very nice.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 31,
      "start_time": 104158.0,
      "end_time": 109853.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 32,
      "start_time": 109853.0,
      "end_time": 113482.0,
      "text": "That attitude of only taking what you need"
    },
    {
      "index": 33,
      "start_time": 113482.0,
      "end_time": 117526.0,
      "text": "was really what everybody had on the network in those days,"
    },
    {
      "index": 34,
      "start_time": 117526.0,
      "end_time": 120823.0,
      "text": "and in fact, it wasn&#39;t just the people on the network,"
    },
    {
      "index": 35,
      "start_time": 120823.0,
      "end_time": 123542.0,
      "text": "but it was actually kind of built into the protocols"
    },
    {
      "index": 36,
      "start_time": 123543.0,
      "end_time": 125487.0,
      "text": "of the Internet itself."
    },
    {
      "index": 37,
      "start_time": 125487.0,
      "end_time": 129346.0,
      "text": "So the basic idea of I.P., or Internet protocol,"
    },
    {
      "index": 38,
      "start_time": 129346.0,
      "end_time": 133750.0,
      "text": "and the way that the -- the routing algorithm that used it,"
    },
    {
      "index": 39,
      "start_time": 133750.0,
      "end_time": 137203.0,
      "text": "were fundamentally \"from each according to their ability,"
    },
    {
      "index": 40,
      "start_time": 137204.0,
      "end_time": 139322.0,
      "text": "to each according to their need.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 41,
      "start_time": 139322.0,
      "end_time": 142335.0,
      "text": "And so, if you had some extra bandwidth,"
    },
    {
      "index": 42,
      "start_time": 142335.0,
      "end_time": 143778.0,
      "text": "you&#39;d deliver a message for someone."
    },
    {
      "index": 43,
      "start_time": 143778.0,
      "end_time": 146771.0,
      "text": "If they had some extra bandwidth, they would deliver a message for you."
    },
    {
      "index": 44,
      "start_time": 146771.0,
      "end_time": 148785.0,
      "text": "You&#39;d kind of depend on people to do that,"
    },
    {
      "index": 45,
      "start_time": 148785.0,
      "end_time": 151448.0,
      "text": "and that was the building block."
    },
    {
      "index": 46,
      "start_time": 151449.0,
      "end_time": 154760.0,
      "text": "It was actually interesting that such a communist principle"
    },
    {
      "index": 47,
      "start_time": 154760.0,
      "end_time": 156512.0,
      "text": "was the basis of a system developed during the Cold War"
    },
    {
      "index": 48,
      "start_time": 156512.0,
      "end_time": 158943.0,
      "text": "by the Defense Department,"
    },
    {
      "index": 49,
      "start_time": 158943.0,
      "end_time": 162130.0,
      "text": "but it obviously worked really well,"
    },
    {
      "index": 50,
      "start_time": 162130.0,
      "end_time": 165456.0,
      "text": "and we all saw what happened with the Internet."
    },
    {
      "index": 51,
      "start_time": 165456.0,
      "end_time": 167727.0,
      "text": "It was incredibly successful."
    },
    {
      "index": 52,
      "start_time": 167728.0,
      "end_time": 171250.0,
      "text": "In fact, it was so successful that there&#39;s no way"
    },
    {
      "index": 53,
      "start_time": 171250.0,
      "end_time": 174613.0,
      "text": "that these days you could make a book like this."
    },
    {
      "index": 54,
      "start_time": 174613.0,
      "end_time": 180779.0,
      "text": "My rough calculation is it would be about 25 miles thick."
    },
    {
      "index": 55,
      "start_time": 180779.0,
      "end_time": 181953.0,
      "text": "But, of course, you couldn&#39;t do it,"
    },
    {
      "index": 56,
      "start_time": 181953.0,
      "end_time": 183743.0,
      "text": "because we don&#39;t know the names of all the people"
    },
    {
      "index": 57,
      "start_time": 183743.0,
      "end_time": 186817.0,
      "text": "with Internet or email addresses,"
    },
    {
      "index": 58,
      "start_time": 186817.0,
      "end_time": 188349.0,
      "text": "and even if we did know their names,"
    },
    {
      "index": 59,
      "start_time": 188349.0,
      "end_time": 190781.0,
      "text": "I&#39;m pretty sure that they would not want their name,"
    },
    {
      "index": 60,
      "start_time": 190782.0,
      "end_time": 195780.0,
      "text": "address and telephone number published to everyone."
    },
    {
      "index": 61,
      "start_time": 195780.0,
      "end_time": 198780.0,
      "text": "So the fact is that there&#39;s a lot of bad guys on the Internet these days,"
    },
    {
      "index": 62,
      "start_time": 198780.0,
      "end_time": 202951.0,
      "text": "and so we dealt with that by making"
    },
    {
      "index": 63,
      "start_time": 202951.0,
      "end_time": 204850.0,
      "text": "walled communities,"
    },
    {
      "index": 64,
      "start_time": 204850.0,
      "end_time": 209587.0,
      "text": "secure subnetworks, VPNs,"
    },
    {
      "index": 65,
      "start_time": 209587.0,
      "end_time": 211183.0,
      "text": "little things that aren&#39;t really the Internet"
    },
    {
      "index": 66,
      "start_time": 211183.0,
      "end_time": 213154.0,
      "text": "but are made out of the same building blocks,"
    },
    {
      "index": 67,
      "start_time": 213154.0,
      "end_time": 215394.0,
      "text": "but we&#39;re still basically building it out of those"
    },
    {
      "index": 68,
      "start_time": 215394.0,
      "end_time": 219661.0,
      "text": "same building blocks with those same assumptions of trust."
    },
    {
      "index": 69,
      "start_time": 219661.0,
      "end_time": 222383.0,
      "text": "And that means that it&#39;s vulnerable"
    },
    {
      "index": 70,
      "start_time": 222383.0,
      "end_time": 224779.0,
      "text": "to certain kinds of mistakes that can happen,"
    },
    {
      "index": 71,
      "start_time": 224779.0,
      "end_time": 226640.0,
      "text": "or certain kinds of deliberate attacks,"
    },
    {
      "index": 72,
      "start_time": 226640.0,
      "end_time": 229744.0,
      "text": "but even the mistakes can be bad."
    },
    {
      "index": 73,
      "start_time": 229745.0,
      "end_time": 232694.0,
      "text": "So, for instance,"
    },
    {
      "index": 74,
      "start_time": 232694.0,
      "end_time": 234647.0,
      "text": "in all of Asia recently,"
    },
    {
      "index": 75,
      "start_time": 234647.0,
      "end_time": 238790.0,
      "text": "it was impossible to get YouTube for a little while"
    },
    {
      "index": 76,
      "start_time": 238800.0,
      "end_time": 240360.0,
      "text": "because Pakistan made some mistakes"
    },
    {
      "index": 77,
      "start_time": 240360.0,
      "end_time": 244950.0,
      "text": "in how it was censoring YouTube in its internal network."
    },
    {
      "index": 78,
      "start_time": 244950.0,
      "end_time": 247189.0,
      "text": "They didn&#39;t intend to screw up Asia, but they did"
    },
    {
      "index": 79,
      "start_time": 247189.0,
      "end_time": 250930.0,
      "text": "because of the way that the protocols work."
    },
    {
      "index": 80,
      "start_time": 250930.0,
      "end_time": 253316.0,
      "text": "Another example that may have affected many of you in this audience is,"
    },
    {
      "index": 81,
      "start_time": 253317.0,
      "end_time": 255908.0,
      "text": "you may remember a couple of years ago,"
    },
    {
      "index": 82,
      "start_time": 255908.0,
      "end_time": 258721.0,
      "text": "all the planes west of the Mississippi were grounded"
    },
    {
      "index": 83,
      "start_time": 258721.0,
      "end_time": 261613.0,
      "text": "because a single routing card in Salt Lake City"
    },
    {
      "index": 84,
      "start_time": 261613.0,
      "end_time": 263975.0,
      "text": "had a bug in it."
    },
    {
      "index": 85,
      "start_time": 263975.0,
      "end_time": 266248.0,
      "text": "Now, you don&#39;t really think"
    },
    {
      "index": 86,
      "start_time": 266248.0,
      "end_time": 269274.0,
      "text": "that our airplane system depends on the Internet,"
    },
    {
      "index": 87,
      "start_time": 269274.0,
      "end_time": 270280.0,
      "text": "and in some sense it doesn&#39;t."
    },
    {
      "index": 88,
      "start_time": 270280.0,
      "end_time": 271895.0,
      "text": "I&#39;ll come back to that later."
    },
    {
      "index": 89,
      "start_time": 271896.0,
      "end_time": 274146.0,
      "text": "But the fact is that people couldn&#39;t take off"
    },
    {
      "index": 90,
      "start_time": 274146.0,
      "end_time": 276421.0,
      "text": "because something was going wrong on the Internet,"
    },
    {
      "index": 91,
      "start_time": 276421.0,
      "end_time": 278996.0,
      "text": "and the router card was down."
    },
    {
      "index": 92,
      "start_time": 278996.0,
      "end_time": 282775.0,
      "text": "And so, there are many of those things that start to happen."
    },
    {
      "index": 93,
      "start_time": 282775.0,
      "end_time": 285914.0,
      "text": "Now, there was an interesting thing that happened last April."
    },
    {
      "index": 94,
      "start_time": 285914.0,
      "end_time": 287440.0,
      "text": "All of a sudden,"
    },
    {
      "index": 95,
      "start_time": 287440.0,
      "end_time": 290772.0,
      "text": "a very large percentage of the traffic on the whole Internet,"
    },
    {
      "index": 96,
      "start_time": 290772.0,
      "end_time": 294903.0,
      "text": "including a lot of the traffic between U.S. military installations,"
    },
    {
      "index": 97,
      "start_time": 294903.0,
      "end_time": 297671.0,
      "text": "started getting re-routed through China."
    },
    {
      "index": 98,
      "start_time": 297671.0,
      "end_time": 300393.0,
      "text": "So for a few hours, it all passed through China."
    },
    {
      "index": 99,
      "start_time": 300393.0,
      "end_time": 304967.0,
      "text": "Now, China Telecom says it was just an honest mistake,"
    },
    {
      "index": 100,
      "start_time": 304967.0,
      "end_time": 308824.0,
      "text": "and it is actually possible that it was, the way things work,"
    },
    {
      "index": 101,
      "start_time": 308824.0,
      "end_time": 310859.0,
      "text": "but certainly somebody could make"
    },
    {
      "index": 102,
      "start_time": 310859.0,
      "end_time": 314132.0,
      "text": "a dishonest mistake of that sort if they wanted to,"
    },
    {
      "index": 103,
      "start_time": 314132.0,
      "end_time": 317490.0,
      "text": "and it shows you how vulnerable the system is even to mistakes."
    },
    {
      "index": 104,
      "start_time": 317490.0,
      "end_time": 322411.0,
      "text": "Imagine how vulnerable the system is to deliberate attacks."
    },
    {
      "index": 105,
      "start_time": 322411.0,
      "end_time": 325809.0,
      "text": "So if somebody really wanted to attack the United States"
    },
    {
      "index": 106,
      "start_time": 325809.0,
      "end_time": 327901.0,
      "text": "or Western civilization these days,"
    },
    {
      "index": 107,
      "start_time": 327901.0,
      "end_time": 330900.0,
      "text": "they&#39;re not going to do it with tanks."
    },
    {
      "index": 108,
      "start_time": 330900.0,
      "end_time": 332503.0,
      "text": "That will not succeed."
    },
    {
      "index": 109,
      "start_time": 332503.0,
      "end_time": 334506.0,
      "text": "What they&#39;ll probably do is something"
    },
    {
      "index": 110,
      "start_time": 334506.0,
      "end_time": 337796.0,
      "text": "very much like the attack that happened"
    },
    {
      "index": 111,
      "start_time": 337797.0,
      "end_time": 340504.0,
      "text": "on the Iranian nuclear facility."
    },
    {
      "index": 112,
      "start_time": 340504.0,
      "end_time": 342778.0,
      "text": "Nobody has claimed credit for that."
    },
    {
      "index": 113,
      "start_time": 342778.0,
      "end_time": 346285.0,
      "text": "There was basically a factory of industrial machines."
    },
    {
      "index": 114,
      "start_time": 346285.0,
      "end_time": 348862.0,
      "text": "It didn&#39;t think of itself as being on the Internet."
    },
    {
      "index": 115,
      "start_time": 348862.0,
      "end_time": 351449.0,
      "text": "It thought of itself as being disconnected from the Internet,"
    },
    {
      "index": 116,
      "start_time": 351449.0,
      "end_time": 353396.0,
      "text": "but it was possible for somebody to smuggle"
    },
    {
      "index": 117,
      "start_time": 353396.0,
      "end_time": 355928.0,
      "text": "a USB drive in there, or something like that,"
    },
    {
      "index": 118,
      "start_time": 355928.0,
      "end_time": 359324.0,
      "text": "and software got in there that causes the centrifuges,"
    },
    {
      "index": 119,
      "start_time": 359324.0,
      "end_time": 362317.0,
      "text": "in that case, to actually destroy themselves."
    },
    {
      "index": 120,
      "start_time": 362317.0,
      "end_time": 364983.0,
      "text": "Now that same kind of software could destroy an oil refinery"
    },
    {
      "index": 121,
      "start_time": 364983.0,
      "end_time": 369405.0,
      "text": "or a pharmaceutical factory or a semiconductor plant."
    },
    {
      "index": 122,
      "start_time": 369405.0,
      "end_time": 372671.0,
      "text": "And so there&#39;s a lot of -- I&#39;m sure you&#39;ve read a lot in papers,"
    },
    {
      "index": 123,
      "start_time": 372671.0,
      "end_time": 374861.0,
      "text": "about worries about cyberattacks"
    },
    {
      "index": 124,
      "start_time": 374862.0,
      "end_time": 377472.0,
      "text": "and defenses against those."
    },
    {
      "index": 125,
      "start_time": 377472.0,
      "end_time": 379452.0,
      "text": "But the fact is, people are mostly focused on"
    },
    {
      "index": 126,
      "start_time": 379452.0,
      "end_time": 381735.0,
      "text": "defending the computers on the Internet,"
    },
    {
      "index": 127,
      "start_time": 381735.0,
      "end_time": 384121.0,
      "text": "and there&#39;s been surprisingly little attention"
    },
    {
      "index": 128,
      "start_time": 384121.0,
      "end_time": 388486.0,
      "text": "to defending the Internet itself as a communications medium."
    },
    {
      "index": 129,
      "start_time": 388486.0,
      "end_time": 390349.0,
      "text": "And I think we probably do need to pay"
    },
    {
      "index": 130,
      "start_time": 390349.0,
      "end_time": 393437.0,
      "text": "some more attention to that, because it&#39;s actually kind of fragile."
    },
    {
      "index": 131,
      "start_time": 393437.0,
      "end_time": 396364.0,
      "text": "So actually, in the early days,"
    },
    {
      "index": 132,
      "start_time": 396364.0,
      "end_time": 398870.0,
      "text": "back when it was the ARPANET,"
    },
    {
      "index": 133,
      "start_time": 398880.0,
      "end_time": 401677.0,
      "text": "there were actually times -- there was a particular time it failed completely"
    },
    {
      "index": 134,
      "start_time": 401677.0,
      "end_time": 404962.0,
      "text": "because one single message processor"
    },
    {
      "index": 135,
      "start_time": 404962.0,
      "end_time": 407438.0,
      "text": "actually got a bug in it."
    },
    {
      "index": 136,
      "start_time": 407438.0,
      "end_time": 409710.0,
      "text": "And the way the Internet works is"
    },
    {
      "index": 137,
      "start_time": 409710.0,
      "end_time": 413277.0,
      "text": "the routers are basically exchanging information"
    },
    {
      "index": 138,
      "start_time": 413277.0,
      "end_time": 415866.0,
      "text": "about how they can get messages to places,"
    },
    {
      "index": 139,
      "start_time": 415867.0,
      "end_time": 419765.0,
      "text": "and this one processor, because of a broken card,"
    },
    {
      "index": 140,
      "start_time": 419765.0,
      "end_time": 421774.0,
      "text": "decided it could actually get a message"
    },
    {
      "index": 141,
      "start_time": 421774.0,
      "end_time": 424462.0,
      "text": "to some place in negative time."
    },
    {
      "index": 142,
      "start_time": 424462.0,
      "end_time": 428445.0,
      "text": "So, in other words, it claimed it could deliver a message before you sent it."
    },
    {
      "index": 143,
      "start_time": 428445.0,
      "end_time": 431594.0,
      "text": "So of course, the fastest way to get a message anywhere"
    },
    {
      "index": 144,
      "start_time": 431595.0,
      "end_time": 433471.0,
      "text": "was to send it to this guy,"
    },
    {
      "index": 145,
      "start_time": 433471.0,
      "end_time": 437180.0,
      "text": "who would send it back in time and get it there super early,"
    },
    {
      "index": 146,
      "start_time": 437180.0,
      "end_time": 439873.0,
      "text": "so every message in the Internet"
    },
    {
      "index": 147,
      "start_time": 439874.0,
      "end_time": 443116.0,
      "text": "started getting switched through this one node,"
    },
    {
      "index": 148,
      "start_time": 443116.0,
      "end_time": 444632.0,
      "text": "and of course that clogged everything up."
    },
    {
      "index": 149,
      "start_time": 444632.0,
      "end_time": 446787.0,
      "text": "Everything started breaking."
    },
    {
      "index": 150,
      "start_time": 446787.0,
      "end_time": 448827.0,
      "text": "The interesting thing was, though,"
    },
    {
      "index": 151,
      "start_time": 448827.0,
      "end_time": 450667.0,
      "text": "that the sysadmins were able to fix it,"
    },
    {
      "index": 152,
      "start_time": 450667.0,
      "end_time": 455448.0,
      "text": "but they had to basically turn every single thing on the Internet off."
    },
    {
      "index": 153,
      "start_time": 455449.0,
      "end_time": 456847.0,
      "text": "Now, of course you couldn&#39;t do that today."
    },
    {
      "index": 154,
      "start_time": 456847.0,
      "end_time": 459241.0,
      "text": "I mean, everything off, it&#39;s like"
    },
    {
      "index": 155,
      "start_time": 459241.0,
      "end_time": 461473.0,
      "text": "the service call you get from the cable company,"
    },
    {
      "index": 156,
      "start_time": 461473.0,
      "end_time": 465234.0,
      "text": "except for the whole world."
    },
    {
      "index": 157,
      "start_time": 465234.0,
      "end_time": 467293.0,
      "text": "Now, in fact, they couldn&#39;t do it for a lot of reasons today."
    },
    {
      "index": 158,
      "start_time": 467293.0,
      "end_time": 469915.0,
      "text": "One of the reasons is a lot of their telephones"
    },
    {
      "index": 159,
      "start_time": 469915.0,
      "end_time": 472884.0,
      "text": "use IP protocol and use things like Skype and so on"
    },
    {
      "index": 160,
      "start_time": 472884.0,
      "end_time": 474953.0,
      "text": "that go through the Internet right now,"
    },
    {
      "index": 161,
      "start_time": 474953.0,
      "end_time": 478234.0,
      "text": "and so in fact we&#39;re becoming dependent on it"
    },
    {
      "index": 162,
      "start_time": 478235.0,
      "end_time": 480270.0,
      "text": "for more and more different things,"
    },
    {
      "index": 163,
      "start_time": 480270.0,
      "end_time": 482965.0,
      "text": "like when you take off from LAX,"
    },
    {
      "index": 164,
      "start_time": 482965.0,
      "end_time": 484845.0,
      "text": "you&#39;re really not thinking you&#39;re using the Internet."
    },
    {
      "index": 165,
      "start_time": 484846.0,
      "end_time": 488962.0,
      "text": "When you pump gas, you really don&#39;t think you&#39;re using the Internet."
    },
    {
      "index": 166,
      "start_time": 488962.0,
      "end_time": 491870.0,
      "text": "What&#39;s happening increasingly, though, is these systems"
    },
    {
      "index": 167,
      "start_time": 491870.0,
      "end_time": 492954.0,
      "text": "are beginning to use the Internet."
    },
    {
      "index": 168,
      "start_time": 492954.0,
      "end_time": 496400.0,
      "text": "Most of them aren&#39;t based on the Internet yet,"
    },
    {
      "index": 169,
      "start_time": 496400.0,
      "end_time": 498540.0,
      "text": "but they&#39;re starting to use the Internet for service functions,"
    },
    {
      "index": 170,
      "start_time": 498540.0,
      "end_time": 500445.0,
      "text": "for administrative functions,"
    },
    {
      "index": 171,
      "start_time": 500445.0,
      "end_time": 503508.0,
      "text": "and so if you take something like the cell phone system,"
    },
    {
      "index": 172,
      "start_time": 503508.0,
      "end_time": 507828.0,
      "text": "which is still relatively independent of the Internet for the most part,"
    },
    {
      "index": 173,
      "start_time": 507828.0,
      "end_time": 510787.0,
      "text": "Internet pieces are beginning to sneak into it"
    },
    {
      "index": 174,
      "start_time": 510787.0,
      "end_time": 514591.0,
      "text": "in terms of some of the control and administrative functions,"
    },
    {
      "index": 175,
      "start_time": 514591.0,
      "end_time": 516921.0,
      "text": "and it&#39;s so tempting to use these same building blocks"
    },
    {
      "index": 176,
      "start_time": 516921.00000000006,
      "end_time": 519185.00000000006,
      "text": "because they work so well, they&#39;re cheap,"
    },
    {
      "index": 177,
      "start_time": 519183.99999999994,
      "end_time": 520283.99999999994,
      "text": "they&#39;re repeated, and so on."
    },
    {
      "index": 178,
      "start_time": 520284.0,
      "end_time": 523570.0,
      "text": "So all of our systems, more and more,"
    },
    {
      "index": 179,
      "start_time": 523570.00000000006,
      "end_time": 524837.0,
      "text": "are starting to use the same technology"
    },
    {
      "index": 180,
      "start_time": 524837.0,
      "end_time": 526904.0,
      "text": "and starting to depend on this technology."
    },
    {
      "index": 181,
      "start_time": 526904.0,
      "end_time": 529329.0,
      "text": "And so even a modern rocket ship these days"
    },
    {
      "index": 182,
      "start_time": 529329.0,
      "end_time": 532550.0,
      "text": "actually uses Internet protocol to talk"
    },
    {
      "index": 183,
      "start_time": 532550.0,
      "end_time": 533871.0,
      "text": "from one end of the rocket ship to the other."
    },
    {
      "index": 184,
      "start_time": 533871.0,
      "end_time": 537570.0,
      "text": "That&#39;s crazy. It was never designed to do things like that."
    },
    {
      "index": 185,
      "start_time": 537570.0,
      "end_time": 540174.0,
      "text": "So we&#39;ve built this system"
    },
    {
      "index": 186,
      "start_time": 540174.0,
      "end_time": 543284.0,
      "text": "where we understand all the parts of it,"
    },
    {
      "index": 187,
      "start_time": 543284.0,
      "end_time": 546982.0,
      "text": "but we&#39;re using it in a very, very different way than we expected to use it,"
    },
    {
      "index": 188,
      "start_time": 546982.0,
      "end_time": 549420.0,
      "text": "and it&#39;s gotten a very, very different scale"
    },
    {
      "index": 189,
      "start_time": 549421.0,
      "end_time": 551592.0,
      "text": "than it was designed for."
    },
    {
      "index": 190,
      "start_time": 551592.0,
      "end_time": 554268.0,
      "text": "And in fact, nobody really exactly understands"
    },
    {
      "index": 191,
      "start_time": 554268.0,
      "end_time": 556531.0,
      "text": "all the things it&#39;s being used for right now."
    },
    {
      "index": 192,
      "start_time": 556531.0,
      "end_time": 559340.0,
      "text": "It&#39;s turning into one of these big emergent systems"
    },
    {
      "index": 193,
      "start_time": 559340.0,
      "end_time": 562515.0,
      "text": "like the financial system, where we&#39;ve designed all the parts"
    },
    {
      "index": 194,
      "start_time": 562515.0,
      "end_time": 565121.0,
      "text": "but nobody really exactly understands"
    },
    {
      "index": 195,
      "start_time": 565121.0,
      "end_time": 568348.0,
      "text": "how it operates and all the little details of it"
    },
    {
      "index": 196,
      "start_time": 568348.0,
      "end_time": 571670.0,
      "text": "and what kinds of emergent behaviors it can have."
    },
    {
      "index": 197,
      "start_time": 571670.0,
      "end_time": 574200.0,
      "text": "And so if you hear an expert talking about the Internet"
    },
    {
      "index": 198,
      "start_time": 574200.0,
      "end_time": 576895.0,
      "text": "and saying it can do this, or it does do this, or it will do that,"
    },
    {
      "index": 199,
      "start_time": 576895.0,
      "end_time": 579356.0,
      "text": "you should treat it with the same skepticism"
    },
    {
      "index": 200,
      "start_time": 579356.0,
      "end_time": 583771.0,
      "text": "that you might treat the comments of an economist about the economy"
    },
    {
      "index": 201,
      "start_time": 583771.0,
      "end_time": 586380.0,
      "text": "or a weatherman about the weather, or something like that."
    },
    {
      "index": 202,
      "start_time": 586380.0,
      "end_time": 588686.0,
      "text": "They have an informed opinion,"
    },
    {
      "index": 203,
      "start_time": 588686.0,
      "end_time": 591227.0,
      "text": "but it&#39;s changing so quickly that even the experts"
    },
    {
      "index": 204,
      "start_time": 591227.0,
      "end_time": 593450.0,
      "text": "don&#39;t know exactly what&#39;s going on."
    },
    {
      "index": 205,
      "start_time": 593450.0,
      "end_time": 595737.0,
      "text": "So if you see one of these maps of the Internet,"
    },
    {
      "index": 206,
      "start_time": 595737.0,
      "end_time": 597403.0,
      "text": "it&#39;s just somebody&#39;s guess."
    },
    {
      "index": 207,
      "start_time": 597403.0,
      "end_time": 599601.0,
      "text": "Nobody really knows what the Internet is right now"
    },
    {
      "index": 208,
      "start_time": 599601.0,
      "end_time": 602342.0,
      "text": "because it&#39;s different than it was an hour ago."
    },
    {
      "index": 209,
      "start_time": 602342.0,
      "end_time": 605143.0,
      "text": "It&#39;s constantly changing. It&#39;s constantly reconfiguring."
    },
    {
      "index": 210,
      "start_time": 605143.0,
      "end_time": 606657.0,
      "text": "And the problem with it is,"
    },
    {
      "index": 211,
      "start_time": 606657.0,
      "end_time": 609998.0,
      "text": "I think we are setting ourselves up for a kind of disaster"
    },
    {
      "index": 212,
      "start_time": 609998.0,
      "end_time": 612793.0,
      "text": "like the disaster we had in the financial system,"
    },
    {
      "index": 213,
      "start_time": 612793.0,
      "end_time": 618137.0,
      "text": "where we take a system that&#39;s basically built on trust,"
    },
    {
      "index": 214,
      "start_time": 618137.0,
      "end_time": 620757.0,
      "text": "was basically built for a smaller-scale system,"
    },
    {
      "index": 215,
      "start_time": 620758.0,
      "end_time": 623667.0,
      "text": "and we&#39;ve kind of expanded it way beyond the limits"
    },
    {
      "index": 216,
      "start_time": 623667.0,
      "end_time": 625663.0,
      "text": "of how it was meant to operate."
    },
    {
      "index": 217,
      "start_time": 625663.0,
      "end_time": 628931.0,
      "text": "And so right now, I think it&#39;s literally true"
    },
    {
      "index": 218,
      "start_time": 628931.0,
      "end_time": 632436.0,
      "text": "that we don&#39;t know what the consequences"
    },
    {
      "index": 219,
      "start_time": 632436.0,
      "end_time": 634870.0,
      "text": "of an effective denial-of-service attack"
    },
    {
      "index": 220,
      "start_time": 634870.0,
      "end_time": 636643.0,
      "text": "on the Internet would be,"
    },
    {
      "index": 221,
      "start_time": 636643.0,
      "end_time": 638517.0,
      "text": "and whatever it would be is going to be worse next year,"
    },
    {
      "index": 222,
      "start_time": 638517.0,
      "end_time": 639925.0,
      "text": "and worse next year, and so on."
    },
    {
      "index": 223,
      "start_time": 639925.0,
      "end_time": 642473.0,
      "text": "But so what we need is a plan B."
    },
    {
      "index": 224,
      "start_time": 642474.0,
      "end_time": 644106.0,
      "text": "There is no plan B right now."
    },
    {
      "index": 225,
      "start_time": 644106.0,
      "end_time": 647609.0,
      "text": "There&#39;s no clear backup system that we&#39;ve very carefully kept"
    },
    {
      "index": 226,
      "start_time": 647609.0,
      "end_time": 649555.0,
      "text": "to be independent of the Internet,"
    },
    {
      "index": 227,
      "start_time": 649555.0,
      "end_time": 652621.0,
      "text": "made out of completely different sets of building blocks."
    },
    {
      "index": 228,
      "start_time": 652621.0,
      "end_time": 655634.0,
      "text": "So what we need is something that doesn&#39;t necessarily"
    },
    {
      "index": 229,
      "start_time": 655634.0,
      "end_time": 658368.0,
      "text": "have to have the performance of the Internet,"
    },
    {
      "index": 230,
      "start_time": 658368.0,
      "end_time": 659885.0,
      "text": "but the police department has to be able"
    },
    {
      "index": 231,
      "start_time": 659885.0,
      "end_time": 662408.0,
      "text": "to call up the fire department even without the Internet,"
    },
    {
      "index": 232,
      "start_time": 662408.0,
      "end_time": 664973.0,
      "text": "or the hospitals have to order fuel oil."
    },
    {
      "index": 233,
      "start_time": 664973.0,
      "end_time": 669587.0,
      "text": "This doesn&#39;t need to be a multi-billion-dollar government project."
    },
    {
      "index": 234,
      "start_time": 669587.0,
      "end_time": 672335.0,
      "text": "It&#39;s actually relatively simple to do, technically,"
    },
    {
      "index": 235,
      "start_time": 672335.0,
      "end_time": 676137.0,
      "text": "because it can use existing fibers that are in the ground,"
    },
    {
      "index": 236,
      "start_time": 676137.0,
      "end_time": 678950.0,
      "text": "existing wireless infrastructure."
    },
    {
      "index": 237,
      "start_time": 678960.0,
      "end_time": 680861.0,
      "text": "It&#39;s basically a matter of deciding to do it."
    },
    {
      "index": 238,
      "start_time": 680861.0,
      "end_time": 683345.0,
      "text": "But people won&#39;t decide to do it"
    },
    {
      "index": 239,
      "start_time": 683345.0,
      "end_time": 685724.0,
      "text": "until they recognize the need for it,"
    },
    {
      "index": 240,
      "start_time": 685724.0,
      "end_time": 687222.0,
      "text": "and that&#39;s the problem that we have right now."
    },
    {
      "index": 241,
      "start_time": 687222.0,
      "end_time": 690500.0,
      "text": "So there&#39;s been plenty of people,"
    },
    {
      "index": 242,
      "start_time": 690500.0,
      "end_time": 693490.0,
      "text": "plenty of us have been quietly arguing"
    },
    {
      "index": 243,
      "start_time": 693490.0,
      "end_time": 695967.0,
      "text": "that we should have this independent system for years,"
    },
    {
      "index": 244,
      "start_time": 695967.0,
      "end_time": 698976.0,
      "text": "but it&#39;s very hard to get people focused on plan B"
    },
    {
      "index": 245,
      "start_time": 698976.0,
      "end_time": 702650.0,
      "text": "when plan A seems to be working so well."
    },
    {
      "index": 246,
      "start_time": 702650.0,
      "end_time": 706790.0,
      "text": "So I think that, if people understand"
    },
    {
      "index": 247,
      "start_time": 706790.0,
      "end_time": 709132.0,
      "text": "how much we&#39;re starting to depend on the Internet,"
    },
    {
      "index": 248,
      "start_time": 709133.0,
      "end_time": 711110.0,
      "text": "and how vulnerable it is,"
    },
    {
      "index": 249,
      "start_time": 711110.0,
      "end_time": 713216.0,
      "text": "we could get focused on"
    },
    {
      "index": 250,
      "start_time": 713216.0,
      "end_time": 716240.0,
      "text": "just wanting this other system to exist,"
    },
    {
      "index": 251,
      "start_time": 716240.0,
      "end_time": 719317.0,
      "text": "and I think if enough people say, \"Yeah, I would like to use it,"
    },
    {
      "index": 252,
      "start_time": 719317.0,
      "end_time": 722327.0,
      "text": "I&#39;d like to have such a system,\" then it will get built."
    },
    {
      "index": 253,
      "start_time": 722327.0,
      "end_time": 723750.0,
      "text": "It&#39;s not that hard a problem."
    },
    {
      "index": 254,
      "start_time": 723750.0,
      "end_time": 726985.0,
      "text": "It could definitely be done by people in this room."
    },
    {
      "index": 255,
      "start_time": 726985.0,
      "end_time": 731344.0,
      "text": "And so I think that this is actually,"
    },
    {
      "index": 256,
      "start_time": 731344.0,
      "end_time": 734523.0,
      "text": "of all the problems you&#39;re going to hear about at the conference,"
    },
    {
      "index": 257,
      "start_time": 734523.0,
      "end_time": 737201.0,
      "text": "this is probably one of the very easiest to fix."
    },
    {
      "index": 258,
      "start_time": 737201.0,
      "end_time": 739968.0,
      "text": "So I&#39;m happy to get a chance to tell you about it."
    },
    {
      "index": 259,
      "start_time": 739968.0,
      "end_time": 742579.0,
      "text": "Thank you very much."
    },
    {
      "index": 260,
      "start_time": 742579.0,
      "end_time": 746433.0,
      "text": "(Applause)"
    }
  ]
}